divs: Sighting DetailsScared the heck out of both myself and my wife. At approx 7 pm christmas eve, observed two orange lights slowly hovering overhead. Apparant path was southeast to northeast. witnessed for about 5 minutes before disappearing abruptly. Either the lights dimmed out or the object disappeared. definately was intelligent, both lights flew in a formation and appeared to hover for a few moments.
Summary: Observed two orange UFOs christmas eve, slowly moving overhead for 5 minutes
trends: There has been one other sighting in Schofield
There were no other sightings in Schofield on or around December 24th 2012
